I really want to be part of your crew but sadly I am too young and maybe I won’t have enough confidence to act in front of a camera. I would never forget about my dream to become one member of your awesome family’s. I really respect you, Jianhao, for all the hard work you’ve done. Tests in school are stressing, but it’s always a reward to watch your work every Sunday. I don’t understand why your videos motivate me so much!
I love you Jianhao, and if I had the chance, I would definitely work with you. It’s going to be a pleasure as you’re a man with such good personalities.
I always support you Jianhao, and I wish you support me ( that’s so unbelievable ) because there’s a big literature competition coming on in February.
Good luck in your job!!!
